			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">For the small-scale production scenario, data from Jinchang Cement Group Co., Ltd. in Gansu Province, China, are used. Due to the lack of information on the former, direct atmospheric emission data come from Yunnan Hongda Cement Plant.</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">对于小规模生产情景，使用了来自中国甘肃省金昌水泥集团有限公司的数据。由于前者缺乏信息，因此直接大气排放数据来源于云南宏达水泥厂。</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
